text: Jolien Knollema (born 5 January 2003) is a Dutch volleyball player living in Haren who plays as an outside hitter. She plays since 2018 in Italy. Since 2018 she plays with club Azzurra Volley San Casciano.Jolien Knollema, legavolleyfemminile.it Knollema is member of the Netherlands women's national volleyball team. With the national team she competed at the 2022 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. ==References== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Groningen (city) Category:Sportswomen
